            <description><![CDATA[
<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>**Extra usage tracking** for paid accounts - Track cache creation and extra input tokens with cost calculations</li>
<li>New settings to control extra usage indicators and notifications</li>
<li>Account requirement hint for extra usage feature (requires paid plan with OAuth)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Extra usage cost display now uses dusty plum color for better visual distinction</li>
<li>CMD+Q now quits the app completely (restored standard macOS behavior)</li>
</ul>

See <a href="https://github.com/tartinerlabs/ClaudeMeter/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">CHANGELOG.md</a> for full details.
